[SPEAKER_01] betonski križ sa is...

370
00:15:44,179 --> 00:15:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] nas dočeka raspelo

371
00:15:45,179 --> 00:15:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] na našoj parceli.

372
00:15:46,059 --> 00:15:46,700
[SPEAKER_01] Eto,

373
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:47,860
[SPEAKER_01] sada to je ti odgovor,

374
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

375
00:15:48,179 --> 00:15:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] šta si,

376
00:15:48,559 --> 00:15:50,240
[SPEAKER_01] šta sam se sela

377
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,820
[SPEAKER_01] 12 godina sa djecom,

378
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:53,259
[SPEAKER_01] živjeli ono,

379
00:15:53,259 --> 00:15:54,279
[SPEAKER_01] maltene u autu

380
00:15:54,279 --> 00:15:56,379
[SPEAKER_01] i od bake do bake,

381
00:15:56,379 --> 00:15:57,200
[SPEAKER_01] svašta nešto.

382
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:57,860
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

383
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:58,580
[SPEAKER_01] to je ti odgovor,

384
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] tu sam te čekao

385
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:01,080
[SPEAKER_01] i tu si trebao doći.

386
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] Eto,

387
00:16:01,519 --> 00:16:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo predivno nešto.

388
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:03,759
[SPEAKER_00] Još meni neka susjed

389
00:16:03,759 --> 00:16:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] onak bojažljivo prilazi,

390
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] znate,

391
00:16:05,019 --> 00:16:06,279
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte ga rušiti,

392
00:16:06,279 --> 00:16:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte ga rušiti,

393
00:16:07,059 --> 00:16:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] da, čovječe,

394
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,200
[SPEAKER_00] koga dirne,

395
00:16:08,259 --> 00:16:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] imat će sa mnom problema,

396
00:16:09,139 --> 00:16:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] šta ti čuče,

397
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] tijekao da je to bilo,

398
00:16:11,139 --> 00:16:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] okej.

399
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] E,

400
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] i onda,

401
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno,

402
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Bog tada otvorio,

403
00:16:14,860 --> 00:16:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] samo se krenula gradi kuća.

404
00:16:16,539 --> 00:16:16,879
[SPEAKER_00] To je,

405
00:16:16,879 --> 00:16:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] to je,

406
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] samo su dolazili majstori,

407
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] strojevi,

408
00:16:19,519 --> 00:16:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] novci,

409
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:20,240
[SPEAKER_00] ja,

410
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] ja ni ne znam od kud je to stizalo,

411
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] da me danas pitate,

412
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam.

413
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo dobili kuću,

414
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] koja je po vršinu veća,

415
00:16:25,179 --> 00:16:26,259
[SPEAKER_00] nego svi ti stanovi zajedno,

416
00:16:26,259 --> 00:16:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim,

417
00:16:26,539 --> 00:16:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] što smo ih gledali,

418
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,700
[SPEAKER_00] ali nismo znali zašto je to.

419
00:16:29,019 --> 00:16:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] nismo znali šta Bog s tim misli.

420
00:16:30,340 --> 00:16:32,379
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo za vrijeme gradnje

421
00:16:32,379 --> 00:16:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] te kuće dobili još jedno dijete,

422
00:16:34,059 --> 00:16:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] pa još jedno dijete,

423
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:36,379
[SPEAKER_00] pa se sve onako,

424
00:16:36,379 --> 00:16:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] sobe su se popunjavali.

425
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,120
[SPEAKER_00] I onda,

426
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:41,259
[SPEAKER_00] onda se desila jedna druga epizoda,

427
00:16:41,259 --> 00:16:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] da vam ipak pokažemo

428
00:16:42,299 --> 00:16:43,080
[SPEAKER_00] da je život borba.

429
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] Krenula je korona,

430
00:16:44,559 --> 00:16:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo razdužili stanove,

431
00:16:46,679 --> 00:16:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] iako se kuća skoro napravila,

432
00:16:48,139 --> 00:16:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] odselili smo imocki,

433
00:16:49,659 --> 00:16:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] i onda je se željka baš jako razbolula.

434
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] Posljedice te korone i to sve.

435
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

436
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] hvala Bogu,

437
00:16:56,779 --> 00:16:58,139
[SPEAKER_00] mi se nismo predavali,

438
00:16:58,740 --> 00:16:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] išli smo dalje

439
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] i samo je trebalo još malo uložiti

440
00:17:01,799 --> 00:17:02,919
[SPEAKER_00] da se kuća završi,

441
00:17:02,919 --> 00:17:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] a i vjerovali smo cijelo vrijeme

442
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti s njom sve ok.

443
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam još ti još reći

444
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] samo dvi sitnice kako Bog pomaže.

445
00:17:09,519 --> 00:17:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, jedna od stvari je bilo,

446
00:17:11,619 --> 00:17:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, kad smo trebali napraviti

447
00:17:13,019 --> 00:17:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] samo šahtove za instalaciju

448
00:17:14,339 --> 00:17:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] da se spojimo na kuću,

449
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje majstora.

450
00:17:16,579 --> 00:17:18,240
[SPEAKER_00] Šest mjeseci mi tražimo,

451
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje majstora,

452
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] nigdje nikoga,

453
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] niko ne želi raditi,

454
00:17:20,799 --> 00:17:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] jer je pre mali posao.

455
00:17:21,759 --> 00:17:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, u to vrijeme

456
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] je bila vrlo teška nam situacija,

457
00:17:25,559 --> 00:17:27,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer smo, ja i troje djeca,

458
00:17:27,079 --> 00:17:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] živjeli u Dalmaciji,

459
00:17:28,279 --> 00:17:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] a oni i najstariji sin

460
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji je tada bio školarac,

461
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,279
[SPEAKER_01] su živjeli u Zagrebu,

462
00:17:33,279 --> 00:17:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] u garsonjeri njegovog brata,

463
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] ili su živjeli u toj nedovršenoj kući

464
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] bez struje vode.

465
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:40,839
[SPEAKER_01] To je bila vrlo teška situacija

466
00:17:40,839 --> 00:17:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo mi, naravno,

467
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] htjeli napokon opet živjeti zajedno

468
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] kao obitelj,

469
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] međutim, nismo imali šahtove,

470
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,259
[SPEAKER_01] nismo imali vodu,

471
00:17:49,259 --> 00:17:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] nismo imali struju.

472
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:52,359
[SPEAKER_01] To znači da nemaš ni tigrije.

473
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su tamo svokotali.

474
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je bilo hrabro od njih i tada,

475
00:17:56,500 --> 00:18:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali cilj nam je bio opet biti zajedno.

476
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] I onda nastupa naša draga gospa

477
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smo mi rekli ovako,

478
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] nema majstora, mi ne znamo

479
00:18:07,079 --> 00:18:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] kako se ovo može riješiti.

480
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] I kažem ja svom sinu

481
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] koji je jedini tada bio sa mnom u Zagrebu,

482
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo mi gospi negdje na hodačašće

483
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo vidjeti.

484
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sjetim da ima jedna kapela na sljemenu,

485
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] idemo mi jednu nedilju lijepo na sljeme,

486
00:18:20,779 --> 00:18:22,640
[SPEAKER_00] dolje to će biti naši hodačašće,

487
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] dragoj gospi, siguro će se nešto dogoditi.

488
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] Mi tako odemo,

489
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] ponedljak u jutro, 7 sati,

490
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:30,160
[SPEAKER_00] zove mene jedan majstor od ovih

491
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji smo zvali.

492
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,259
[SPEAKER_00] E, znaš šta, ja sam dobio kuću

493
00:18:33,259 --> 00:18:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] za izgradnju 500 metara od vaše,

494
00:18:35,279 --> 00:18:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] mogu napraviti vaš šaht.

495
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] I čovjek samo dođe i napravi ga.

496
00:18:38,799 --> 00:18:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, to je samo jedan primjer

497
00:18:40,119 --> 00:18:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] kako gospa pomaže.

498
00:18:41,079 --> 00:18:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] I onda još samo trebalo spojiti,

499
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] a eto, grad Zagreb nije nikako se odaziva,

500
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] opet par mjeseci,

501
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] i onda mi kažemo,

502
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] evo sveti Jospe, mi ćemo...

503
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj, čekaj.

504
00:18:50,579 --> 00:18:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

505
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] Za laufao se.

506
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

507
00:18:55,619 --> 00:18:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] Pao.

508
00:18:58,099 --> 00:18:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala.

509
00:18:59,619 --> 00:19:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] Uglavnom, naši nama su dolazili oni u Dalmaciju,

510
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:12,880
[SPEAKER_01] Krešo i naš najstariji sin,

511
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] i sin se jednu nedelju užasno rasplakao,

512
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] nije više ti joj ići u Zagreb,

513
00:19:17,059 --> 00:19:18,160
[SPEAKER_01] nije ti joj ići u školu.

514
00:19:18,819 --> 00:19:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vidjela da tu mi više nemamo svoje snage,

515
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] kako će mi natjerat grad, vodovod,

516
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] da nam dovede vodu u tu kuću.

517
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dok su se oni vozili,

518
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,339
[SPEAKER_01] ja mu govorim, znaš šta, Krešo,

519
00:19:30,339 --> 00:19:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] nema nam druge, moramo moliti.

520
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] Molit ćemo, evo ovog čovjeka tu,

521
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelja,

522
00:19:36,140 --> 00:19:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] vama s desne, s lijeve,

523
00:19:38,519 --> 00:19:39,319
[SPEAKER_01] na slici,

524
00:19:39,319 --> 00:19:41,859
[SPEAKER_01] zaštitnika, obitelji,

525
00:19:41,859 --> 00:19:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] očeva, inženjera,

526
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] djece, trudnica,

527
00:19:47,759 --> 00:19:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] najboljega zapitanja,

528
00:19:49,579 --> 00:19:52,140
[SPEAKER_01] zapitanja, rješavanja stambenog pitanja.

529
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:55,299
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo odlučili moliti 30-odnevnicu

530
00:19:55,299 --> 00:19:56,279
[SPEAKER_01] Svetom Josipom

531
00:19:56,279 --> 00:19:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] i za vrijeme te 30-odnevnice,

532
00:19:59,359 --> 00:20:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] točnije, ono ne znam,

533
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:01,599
[SPEAKER_01] taj zadnji tjedan,

534
00:20:01,599 --> 00:20:03,240
[SPEAKER_01] sam se ja jako razboljila,

535
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] došla je ta korona,

536
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:04,920
[SPEAKER_01] nesretna,

537
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,259
[SPEAKER_01] ono, sa troje djece

538
00:20:06,259 --> 00:20:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] i malom bebom koje sam i dojela.

539
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] U to vrijeme sam se razboljila

540
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] do te mjere da nisam mogla ništa,

541
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] nisam mogla dignuti žlicu,

542
00:20:13,579 --> 00:20:14,779
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji su me hranili.

543
00:20:14,779 --> 00:20:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] I to je tako sve u tom trenutku,

544
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] znači sve izgledalo kao da se naš život raspada,

545
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] ne, da ćemo mi biti opet zajedno

546
00:20:23,559 --> 00:20:25,240
[SPEAKER_01] ili živjeti u našoj kući zajedno,

547
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] svi djeca su bila tužna

548
00:20:28,099 --> 00:20:28,680
[SPEAKER_01] i tako,

549
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:31,660
[SPEAKER_01] to je baš izgledalo grozno,

550
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] koda je nekakva tragedija na pomolu,

551
00:20:34,819 --> 00:20:36,259
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne nešto dobro.

552
00:20:36,259 --> 00:20:40,720
[SPEAKER_01] I bio je sveti Nikola,

553
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je bio zadnji dan zapravo 30. dnevnice,

554
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ono, to izmolula,

555
00:20:45,039 --> 00:20:48,660
[SPEAKER_01] iako nisam pet dana spavala od te korone,

556
00:20:48,660 --> 00:20:50,940
[SPEAKER_01] izmolula sam nekako,

557
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] nemam pojma na koji način,

558
00:20:53,019 --> 00:20:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] čula sam se s njim na večer,

559
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,220
[SPEAKER_01] on je umirivo sina

560
00:20:57,220 --> 00:20:59,200
[SPEAKER_01] i evo, on može sad još.

561
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo mi izmolili,

562
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] ja i on u Zagrebu,

563
00:21:02,339 --> 00:21:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] zadnju večer tu u 30. dnevnicu,

564
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] i onako sam baš iz srca rekao,

565
00:21:06,839 --> 00:21:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] sveto mi Jospe,

566
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sveti Jospe,

567
00:21:08,319 --> 00:21:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne radi mene,

568
00:21:09,079 --> 00:21:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] radi ovog djeteta,

569
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] samo radi ovog djeteta,

570
00:21:11,380 --> 00:21:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] pokaži da možeš.

571
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] I otišli smo spavali,

572
00:21:15,140 --> 00:21:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] ujutro 7 sati,

573
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:18,660
[SPEAKER_00] opet zoni mobita.

574
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:20,359
[SPEAKER_00] Reko, daj me nemoj,

575
00:21:20,359 --> 00:21:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] ko je sad?

576
00:21:21,079 --> 00:21:24,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, mi smo došli iz grada Zagreba,

577
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] di je ta voda,

578
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] di treba spojiti,

579
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] što treba spojiti?

580
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] Dragom Bogu,

581
00:21:27,839 --> 00:21:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je nevjerojatno.

582
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,339
[SPEAKER_00] Svetom Josipu, hvala.

583
00:21:30,339 --> 00:21:32,359
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko smo samo u tim trenutcima

584
00:21:32,359 --> 00:21:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] osjećali njihovu potporu.

585
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,839
[SPEAKER_00] I svoji mi sad završili

586
00:21:35,839 --> 00:21:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako je Bog rješio naše probleme

587
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] i kako je Bog nas doveo

588
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] do mjesta gdje ne se želo.

589
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo sad presretni u toj kući.

590
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] A šta je tu ključno bilo po meni?

591
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je od uvijek znao

592
00:21:46,339 --> 00:21:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo imati puno djece,

593
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ih treba smjestiti.

594
00:21:50,019 --> 00:21:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] I dao nam je posao

595
00:21:51,359 --> 00:21:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] da radimo od doma,

596
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:54,319
[SPEAKER_00] da imamo vremena za njih,

597
00:21:54,319 --> 00:21:55,839
[SPEAKER_00] da su mama i tata uvijek doma,

598
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] da uvijek može biti skuhano,

599
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,359
[SPEAKER_00] da uvijek može biti opravano,

600
00:21:58,359 --> 00:21:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] da uvijek nas mogu zagrli,

601
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] da ju uvijek možemo dočekati.

602
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] I to je onaj način koji smo vam htjeli reći

603
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] kako je Bogu sve moguće,

604
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] čak i u današnje vrijeme.

605
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte se bojati ničega.

606
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno sve može,

607
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,839
[SPEAKER_00] samo se utječite dragom Bogu.

608
00:22:10,839 --> 00:22:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je sto posto tako.

609
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to vam i možemo

610
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] i našeg primjera posljedočiti.

611
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, i sad još samo,

612
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] evo, pošto je tema ljubav,

613
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi o tome mogli nešto reći.

614
00:22:20,799 --> 00:22:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ćeš ti prva.

615
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mi kad smo razmišljali o toj temi ljubavi,

616
00:22:24,519 --> 00:22:25,700
[SPEAKER_01] mislili smo, pa dobro,

617
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] šta nećemo sad nas dvoje tu stati i govoriti,

618
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,680
[SPEAKER_01] pa dobro, ja njega volim,

619
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] on mene voli.

620
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:32,180
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je valjda jasno

621
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom na broj djece.

622
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim, stvarno ono u braku,

623
00:22:41,460 --> 00:22:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] i što je Frad Stjepan govorio u propovjedi,

624
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] nema bez žrtve.

625
00:22:45,559 --> 00:22:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] To je tajna ljubav.

626
00:22:47,900 --> 00:22:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] To stvarno, moraš se odreći samog sebe,

627
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:52,799
[SPEAKER_01] zaista, svega svoga i ambicije,

628
00:22:52,799 --> 00:22:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] i svega, i muškarci, i žene.

629
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:56,700
[SPEAKER_01] Žedama je možda lakše,

630
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer one su inkubator,

631
00:22:58,579 --> 00:23:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] kad si trudna, jednostavno se totalno

632
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] prepustiš čuvanju tog djeteta,

633
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] i nekako prirodno ti dođe

634
00:23:06,559 --> 00:23:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] da se odrekneš svega.

635
00:23:08,579 --> 00:23:10,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ali muškarcima je to teže još.

636
00:23:10,279 --> 00:23:12,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, vjerujte mi, isplaci se.

637
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:14,859
[SPEAKER_01] I koliko će vas žena voljeti više

638
00:23:14,859 --> 00:23:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] kad vidi da ju vi podupirete,

639
00:23:17,059 --> 00:23:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] da ne sjedite vani sa dečkima na pivi,

640
00:23:21,759 --> 00:23:23,200
[SPEAKER_01] nego da ste doma sa njom,

641
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] ili da ju pomažete oko djeteta.

642
00:23:25,180 --> 00:23:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte, bit ćete radosni cijeli život

643
00:23:28,059 --> 00:23:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] dečki s time.

644
00:23:29,619 --> 00:23:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ali razmišljali smo o tome

645
00:23:32,519 --> 00:23:33,640
[SPEAKER_01] što je nama bila ljubav,

646
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] i onda nam je samo došlo više

647
00:23:35,539 --> 00:23:38,700
[SPEAKER_01] kako smo mi kroz naš život

648
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:41,819
[SPEAKER_01] i to dobivanje djece i svega

649
00:23:41,819 --> 00:23:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] osjećali od drugih ljudi ljubav.

650
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] A to je jedna velika zajednica,

651
00:23:47,079 --> 00:23:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] veća zajednica,

652
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] kroz sve te teškoće koje smo mi prolazili,

653
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] nama je obitelj naša bila

654
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,299
[SPEAKER_01] jako sklonao.

655
00:23:55,299 --> 00:23:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, kad pitam sama sebe što je to ljubav,

656
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ja osjetila ljubav,

657
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] a po meni su to tako,

658
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] ono, to možda stvari koje iskipaćamo zdravo zagotovo,

659
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:08,240
[SPEAKER_01] ali koje su,

660
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:10,680
[SPEAKER_01] koje ti stvarno daju snago.

661
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti, na primjer,

662
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:14,660
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti sve krova pošalje lona carne

663
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:16,160
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne znam, galon raštike,

664
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti mama bolesna,

665
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] ima isto koronu,

666
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali diže se iz kreveta i kaže,

667
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:24,319
[SPEAKER_01] gle, ja ću sad čuvat tebe i tvoje troje djece.

668
00:24:24,319 --> 00:24:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja je kažem, mama,

669
00:24:25,119 --> 00:24:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] ajde u kreveć, šta ti je?

670
00:24:26,799 --> 00:24:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ti imaš 70 godina,

671
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne imam toliko.

672
00:24:29,619 --> 00:24:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želim ono da umreš.

673
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ona govori, pa šta je meni,

674
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] šta sam ja sebi bitna?

675
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:39,160
[SPEAKER_01] Pa bitnija si mi ti i tvoja djeca od mene sami.

676
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:43,339
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda kad ti did ko ima 70 godina

677
00:24:43,339 --> 00:24:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] sjedne u Dalmaciji u auto,

678
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:46,859
[SPEAKER_01] vozi tri sata

679
00:24:46,859 --> 00:24:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ti doveze auto,

680
00:24:48,619 --> 00:24:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer zna da se tvoj pokvario

681
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] i da ne možeš razvazati djecu

682
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] u školu vrtičnom,

683
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,819
[SPEAKER_01] tisuću obaveza.

684
00:24:53,819 --> 00:24:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sjedne u auto čovjek

685
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:59,319
[SPEAKER_01] i doveze ti auto u 70 godina.

686
00:24:59,319 --> 00:25:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti svetstra dođe iz Zadra,

687
00:25:01,779 --> 00:25:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] vas sedam u kući,

688
00:25:03,619 --> 00:25:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] povraća i ima koronu

689
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,660
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne znam šta,

690
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:09,160
[SPEAKER_01] ona dođe i kuhat za tebe,

691
00:25:09,319 --> 00:25:10,720
[SPEAKER_01] tvoju djecu, čuva djecu.

692
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kad, ne znam,

693
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] neoženjeni stric,

694
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] uzmeti tvoje troje djece,

695
00:25:15,900 --> 00:25:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači ne znam ni pelenu presuć

696
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] i dovedeti ih u Zagrebi,

697
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] zimutskog.

698
00:25:20,359 --> 00:25:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

699
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:23,259
[SPEAKER_01] to su neke,

700
00:25:23,259 --> 00:25:24,819
[SPEAKER_01] to su situacije,

701
00:25:24,819 --> 00:25:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili recimo,

702
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,660
[SPEAKER_01] kad nam je bilo najteže,

703
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:27,779
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo oboje bili

704
00:25:27,779 --> 00:25:29,160
[SPEAKER_01] bolestni,

705
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] a bilo je i takvih situacija,

706
00:25:30,599 --> 00:25:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo jednu dadilju,

707
00:25:33,279 --> 00:25:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] ona se pretvorila u hobotnicu.

708
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:35,640
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

709
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] pere,

710
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] kuha,

711
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:37,900
[SPEAKER_01] nabavlja namirnice,

712
00:25:37,900 --> 00:25:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] djecu tušira,

713
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,819
[SPEAKER_01] meni pere kosu

714
00:25:41,819 --> 00:25:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

715
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] To su sve te neke situacije

716
00:25:45,579 --> 00:25:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem ti osjetiš

717
00:25:47,579 --> 00:25:49,059
[SPEAKER_01] ono da si voljen

718
00:25:49,059 --> 00:25:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] i to ti je zapravo ljubav.

719
00:25:51,079 --> 00:25:51,319
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

720
00:25:51,319 --> 00:25:53,180
[SPEAKER_01] to što ja osjećam da je ljubava,

721
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] to je ono

722
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] kad Sveti Pavao govori

723
00:25:56,380 --> 00:25:58,380
[SPEAKER_01] što je ljubav ili što nije

724
00:25:58,380 --> 00:25:59,640
[SPEAKER_01] i kad kaže

725
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] a meni najviše uvijek ono ostane

726
00:26:01,579 --> 00:26:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne traži svoje.

727
00:26:04,539 --> 00:26:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

728
00:26:06,599 --> 00:26:08,759
[SPEAKER_01] svi ti ljudi koji su nama pomagali,

729
00:26:08,759 --> 00:26:11,220
[SPEAKER_01] oni su se sebe odrekli

730
00:26:11,220 --> 00:26:12,839
[SPEAKER_01] da nama to vrijeme daju

731
00:26:12,839 --> 00:26:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] i da nama pomognu

732
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad mi nismo mogli sami.

733
00:26:16,039 --> 00:26:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] A Bog ti uvijek tako i šalje ljude

734
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,799
[SPEAKER_01] i mame i tate i djedove

735
00:26:20,799 --> 00:26:22,740
[SPEAKER_01] i stričeve i sestre

736
00:26:22,740 --> 00:26:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] i ne poznate ljude

737
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,779
[SPEAKER_01] da te podrže

738
00:26:26,779 --> 00:26:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] i mi kad smo i mislili

739
00:26:28,940 --> 00:26:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] da nam je najteže

740
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:31,740
[SPEAKER_01] da naša obitelj će propasti

741
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] i raspasti se,

742
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,759
[SPEAKER_01] nikad se to na kraju nije dogodilo.

743
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tu stojimo pred vama,

744
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:38,880
[SPEAKER_01] živi, zdravi, radosni

745
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:41,759
[SPEAKER_01] i...

746
00:26:41,759 --> 00:26:44,200
[SPEAKER_00] I da čekamo se vrati svoji djeci.

747
00:26:44,359 --> 00:26:46,240
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, hvala vam, evo, hvala vam

748
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] što ste nas postišali i to...

749
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala što pratite kanal.

